  "text": "On the other hand, a recent study [CITATION_1] tackles this problem by suggesting various objective performance metrics for evaluating Arabic OCR systems which can provide us with more insight into the effectiveness of Arabic OCR systems. Therefore, the current study adopts these metrics to evaluate the performance of Arabic OCR systems. The adopted performance metrics are defined in the following subsections.",
